<div class="row">

  <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 text-center">
    <% if params[:plan] == '2' %>
      <h1>Pro Account</h1>
      <p>Artists and A&amp;R's should sign up for the Pro account. When you choose this option, artists have the chance to upload music and be heard by A&amp;R's. A&amp;R's have the opportunity to find their next big artist. Let us get you connected!</p>
    <% else %>
      <h1>Basic Account</h1>
      <p>Lovers of new music should choose the Basic account. This will give you an unlimited number of new songs being uploaded by artists everyday to discover, all for the low price of Free.</p>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
    <div class="well">
      <h2>Sign up</h2>

      <% if params[:plan] == '2' %>
        <%= render "pro_form" %>
      <% else %>
        <%= render "basic_form" %>
      <% end %>

      <%= render "devise/shared/links" %>
    </div>
  </div>
  
</div>